'''Rómendacil''', [[Quenya]] for "East-victor", can refer to two [[Gondorians|Gondorian]] kings:
* [[Rómendacil I]] ({{TA|310}} - {{TA|541|n}}), born [[Tarostar]], the eighth [[Kings of Gondor|King]] of [[Gondor]].
* [[Rómendacil II]] ({{TA|1126}} - {{TA|1366|n}}), born [[Minalcar]], the nineteenth [[Kings of Gondor|King]] of [[Gondor]].
